OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine and chilly to start with
OL,6,Fsome sunshine, however cloud soon
OL,7,Fthickening from the west. Staying
OL,8,Fmainly dry but becoming generally
OL,9,Frather cloudy during the afternoon,
OL,10,Fwith winds strengthening. Mild in
OL,11,Fshelter.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBecoming windy, with inland
OL,14,Fgales, coupled with heavy rain and
OL,15,Fblustery showers moving into the north
OL,16,Fof the region especially. Less windy
OL,17,Fbut rather cloudy and wet by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
