OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cloudy and wet start for
OL,6,Fmany, however becoming drier and
OL,7,Fbrighter from the southwest as the day
OL,8,Fdevelops, with eventual sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping widely. Feeling cooler but
OL,10,Fless windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,13,Ffine through this period, with some
OL,14,Fwarm days and sunny periods after
OL,15,Fchilly starts, with a slight frost
OL,16,Fperhaps starting Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
